        jTextArea3.setText("1. A Day in the Life (Lennon/McCartney)\n2. I Want to Hold Your Hand\n3. Strawberry Fields Forever(Lennon)\n4. Yesterday (McCartney)\n5. In My Life (Lennon)\n6. Something (Harrison)\n7. Hey Jude (McCartney)\n8. Let it Be (McCartney)\n9. Come Together (Lennon)\n10. While My Guitar Gently Weeps (Harrison)\n11. A Hard Day’s Night (Lennon)\n12. Norwegian Wood (This Bird Has Flown) (Lennon)\n13. Revolution (Lennon)\n14. She Loves You (Lennon/McCartney)\n15. Help! (Lennon)\n16. I Saw Her Standing There (McCartney/Lennon)\n17. Ticket to Ride (Lennon)\n18. Tomorrow Never Knows (Lennon)\n19. Lucy in the Sky With Diamonds (Lennon)\n20. Please Please Me (Lennon)\n21. All You Need is Love (Lennon)\n22. Eleanor Rigby (McCartney)\n23. Abbey Road Medley (McCartney/Lennon)\n24. Happiness is a Warm Gun (Lennon)\n25. Here, There, and Everywhere (McCartney)\n26. If I Fell (Lennon)\n27. You’re Going to Lose That Girl (Lennon)\n28. Here Comes the Sun (Harrison)\n29. Can’t Buy Me Love (McCartney/Lennon)\n30. We Can Work it Out (McCartney)\n31. You’ve Got to Hide Your Love Away (Lennon)\n32. Penny Lane (McCartney)\n33. I Am the Walrus (Lennon)\n34. Eight Days a Week (Lennon)\n35. Paperback Writer (McCartney)\n 36. I Should Have Known Better (Lennon)\n38. Blackbird (McCartney)\n39. Day Tripper (McCartney/Lennon)\n40. For No One (McCartney)\n41. Get Back (McCartney)\n42. I Feel Fine (Lennon)\n43. Drive My Car (McCartney)\n44. All My Loving (McCartney)\n45. No Reply (Lennon)\n46. Don’t Let Me Down (Lennon)\n47. Things We Said Today (McCartney)\n48. The Ballad of John and Yoko (Lennon)\n49. The Night Before (McCartney)\n50. Got to Get You Into My Life (McCartney)\n51. If I Needed Someone (Harrison)\n52. Helter Skelter (McCartney)\n53. It Won’t Be Long (Lennon)\n54. Two of Us (McCartney/Lennon)\n56. I’m Down (McCartney)\n57. I’m Only Sleeping (Lennon)\n58. I’ve Just Seen a Face (McCartney)\n59. I Want You (She’s So Heavy) (Lennon)\n60. Sgt. Pepper’s Lonely Hearts Club Band (McCartney)\n61. With a Little Help From My Friends (Ringo)\n62. Girl (Lennon)\n63. Dear Prudence (Lennon)\n64. I’ve Got a Feeling (McCartney)\n65. And I Love Her (McCartney)\n66. Nowhere Man (Lennon)\n67. Oh! Darling (McCartney)\n68. Baby, You’re a Rich Man (Lennon)\n69. Julia (Lennon)\n70. You Can’t Do That (Lennon)\n71. I’m a Loser (Lennon)\n72. From Me to You (Lennon/McCartney)\n73. Everybody’s Got Something to Hide Except for Me and My Monkey (Lennon)\n74. Yellow Submarine (Ringo)\n75. Think for Yourself (Harrison)\n76. Yer Blues (Lennon)\n77. Because (Lennon)\n78. And Your Bird Can Sing (Lennon)\n79. I’ll Follow the Sun (McCartney)\n80. Mother Nature’s Son (McCartney)\n81. Hey Bulldog (Lennon)\n82. She’s Leaving Home (McCartney)\n83. I’m So Tired (Lennon)\n84. Across the Universe (Lennon)\n85. Back in the USSR (McCartney)\n86. Lady Madonna (Ringo)\n87. Love Me Do (McCartney)\n88. Rain (Lennon)\n89. Good Day Sunshine (McCarntey)\n90. The Long and Winding Road (McCartney)\n91. Every Little Thing (Lennon)\n92. Dig a Pony (Lennon)\n93. Sexy Sadie (Lennon)\n94. You Won’t See Me (McCartney)\n95. Any Time at All (Lennon)\n96. Within You Without You (Harrison)\n97. All I’ve Got to Do (Lennon)\n98. Long, Long, Long (Harrison)\n99. Yes It Is\n100. Hello, Goodbye (McCartney)");
        jScrollPane3.setViewportView(jTextArea3);

